There is holes that
we're falling into here.

31:32.291 --> 31:33.590
This is this is ice we're on,

31:33.692 --> 31:35.959
look at the way it's going on,
buddy.

31:36.061 --> 31:38.662
(Splashing) I wonder if
anybody's checked this

